            <title><![CDATA[How to fix invalid or corrupted package (PGP signature)issue?]]></title>
            <link>https://wiki.archcraft.io/fr/blog/02-post-pacman</link>
            <guid>https://wiki.archcraft.io/fr/blog/02-post-pacman</guid>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[If you get invalid or corrupted package (PGP signature) error, do :]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you get <code>invalid or corrupted package (PGP signature) error</code>, do :</p>
<ul>
<li>Open a terminal</li>
<li>Run: <code>sudo pacman -S archlinux-keyring</code></li>
<li>Then Run: <code>sudo pacman-key --init</code></li>
<li>Then Run: <code>sudo pacman-key --populate</code></li>
<li>Done! (Also delete the corrupted pkgs too.)</li>
</ul>]]></content:encoded>
