        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[How to add my music in the player?]]></title>
            <link>https://wiki.archcraft.io/fr/blog/01-post-mpd</link>
            <guid>https://wiki.archcraft.io/fr/blog/01-post-mpd</guid>
            <pubDate>Tue, 20 Jul 2021 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[To add your favorite music in mpd, (assuming your songs are stored in ~/Music directory) follow the steps below :]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>To add your favorite music in <code>mpd</code>, (<em>assuming your songs are stored in <code>~/Music</code> directory</em>) follow the steps below :</p>
<ul>
<li>Open a terminal and run <strong>ncmpcpp</strong></li>
<li>In <code>ncmpcpp</code>, press <kbd>2</kbd> to open <strong>song browser</strong></li>
<li>In browser tab, press <kbd>u</kbd> to update the <strong>music database</strong></li>
<li>Select your songs and press <kbd>SPACE</kbd> to add the songs in your <strong>current playlist</strong></li>
<li>Done!</li>
</ul>]]></content:encoded>
